A //Lie algebra// is a vector space $$\mathcal L$$ with a skew-symmetric product
$$
\mathcal L\times \mathcal L\to\mathcal L,\qquad (v,w)\mapsto [v,w]=-[w,v]
$$
which is bilinear and satisfies the //Jacobi identity//
$$
[u,[v,w]]+[v,[w,u]]+[w,[u,v]]=0.
$$